    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个梦境黑色电影风格的故事，剧情是关键 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📌 <strong>《梦境罪行》融合了视觉小说的叙事风格和类似图形冒险游戏的点击解谜玩法。</strong> 在梦境世界中探索犯罪现场，<strong>物品将成为你的唯一证人</strong>。<strong>仔细检查每个角落，收集线索，并决定每位嫌疑人的命运。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.poster.avif?t=1766332152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.webm?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/6de80e3f7bd496f1f38853cad3e3508a.mp4?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>🔎 <strong>六起案件，六桩犯罪……以及一个隐藏其中的秘密。</strong> 看似独立的调查，实际上是一个更庞大谜团的一部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📖 <strong>沉浸在独特的黑色电影氛围中，</strong>体验引人入胜的剧情、巧妙的对话以及一个充满秘密的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚠️ <strong>这不是一款动作游戏，也不是开放式推理体验，而是一款基于叙事探索的互动故事。</strong> 如果你喜欢互动式推理小说，<strong>《梦境罪行》</strong> 一定会让你沉浸其中。<br><br>《梦境罪行》……还是梦境中的罪行？只有你能揭开真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.poster.avif?t=1766332152\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.webm?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341400/extras/a9048b160e896f23f0b38601dab0fb75.mp4?t=1766332152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
